{
  "texts": [
    "Addressing these issues requires more than just setting guidelines; it calls for a holistic approach that includes educating students about AI, its ethical use, and limitations.",
    "To equip both students and teachers to become apt in the use of AI for their academic purposes, a new \"culture of AI\" seems in order.",
    "An AI-culture should permeate academic life, creating an environment where AI is not feared but readily used, understood and -most importantly -critically evaluated.",
    "A potential avenue would be the implementation of regular workshops and meetings for teachers, supervisors, and students.",
    "These sessions should focus on up-to-date AI developments, ethical considerations, and best practices."
  ]
}